  Plan-side findings: (a) context-blind reciprocal `А у тебе?` mandated for a name-exchange in dialogue_situations[1]
  — fixed to the context-appropriate `А тебе?` (elliptical for `А тебе як звати?`); (b) no Russianisms
  in plan prose (scan clean — uses synthetic imperative `Прочитаймо`, no `Давайте`, no `приймати` calques);
  (c) no calques in vocabulary_hints (all VESUM-verified); (d) no plan-internal contradictions (word_target
  sum 300+250+250+250+150 = 1200); (e) added back-reference to LOCKED wiki in references[]. Paired wiki
